5.4 Biology Marking Adapters

The core marking engine handles MCQ and numeric types. Biology adds
these adapters:

  ------------------ ------------------- ------------------ --------------------
  **Answer Type**    **Input Format**    **Marking Rule**   **Partial Credit**

  diagram_label      { \[hotspotId\]:    Exact match per    1 mark per correct
                     termId }            hotspot            label

  process_sequence   \[stepId, stepId,   Correct adjacent   1 mark per correct
                     \...\]              pairs              pair

  keyword_match      { \[blankId\]:      Exact match per    1 mark per correct
                     termId }            blank              term

  punnett_grid       { \[cellId\]:       Case-insensitive   1 mark per correct
                     genotype }          match              cell

  self_assessed      { text,             Student self-marks Based on checklist
                     checkedPoints\[\] }                    ticks
  ------------------ ------------------- ------------------ --------------------

